{"tid":991014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男突然四肢麻痺命危　醫生：因為他吃大量水果","createTime":"2019-01-22T05:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T07:50:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ac70163f9a24b79502af12373f55f6d70e9817c3","tid":991014,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"中國陝西西安一名60多歲的王姓男子，近日突然四肢麻痺，送醫後醫院發出病危通知書。醫生表示，王男是因為服用大量水果，才導致生命危險。<br />\n王男告訴醫生，他於一個禮拜內，吃掉2.5公斤的香蕉，又吃了將近3公斤的柳橙。他以為吃得很健康，沒想到反而吃到住進醫院。<br />\n醫生解釋，王男本身的腎功能不佳，有排鉀障礙。而他大量攝取香蕉、柳橙等含鉀量高的水果，容易出現高鉀血症徵狀，嚴重時會心臟驟停猝死。醫生提醒，酪梨、番茄、紫菜、香菇、木耳、海帶等食物，都含有高含量的鉀，腎病患者，應該盡量避免食用。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190122/640_adbfb9c456733a164db2a0fb89f0e323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190122%2F640_adbfb9c456733a164db2a0fb89f0e323.jpg&h=a831ac4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190122/1504943/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190122%2F1504943%2F&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIp%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a8c5d842\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190122%2F1504943%2F&h=daf1c807\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190122/1504943/</a>"},{"pid":"5e1dfec15263dfbe9659c927e861e2f448a96bad","tid":991014,"uid":210638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"中蕉毒橙毒"},{"pid":"b0724d8949a0b28172c92451aa5a0e29b2e05350","tid":991014,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:26:07.000Z","msg":"其實大陸D蕉同橙可能係假"},{"pid":"b9a874f0e1addd28d90f0dd0fcac181051510750","tid":991014,"uid":89200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"走火入魔"},{"pid":"bba151